CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 4, 1956, pg. 19, reads: On The Scene - Rosalyn King (left), one of the hostesses at the party given by the Little Frogs, gets refreshments from the snack bar for her guests, while some of the boys and girls on hand chat and sip pop. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Young men, and young women, including Rosalyn King holding bottle of soda, standing at bar in Loendi Club for "Little FROGS" party
